lead_paragraph: Southampton's match winner Jay Rodriguez, who scored two goals in a Premier League game for the first time in almost three years to beat local rivals Bournemouth 3-1 on Sunday, praised his team's grit and quality in a dominant second-half performance.

headline.main: Two-Goal Rodriguez Praises Southampton's True Grit
headline.print_headline: Two-Goal Rodriguez Praises Southampton's True Grit
